### Todo endpoints
### Base URL – adjust host/port as needed
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Get all todos  #   
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos
Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get todo by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos/1

### Add todo
POST {{baseUrl}}/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My first todo",
  "completed": false
}

### Update todo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated title",
  "completed": true
}

### Delete todo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/todos/1

